data.title: I'm glad I'm married
data.meta_description: Todd collection.Edison Standard Record: 10018.Words by Jack Norworth.Year of release and songwriting credit from "The Edison Phonograph Monthly," v.6 (1908/1909).Billy Murray.Comic song. Tenor solo with orchestra accompaniment.Also available online via the Internet.
